Data.Name: Push key out of the keyhole

AudioData.Text: If I now push the key it should drop on the sheet of paper. Genius!
Maybe I can stick this pencil somewhere?
Clonk! The key dropped on the paper.
A blank sheet of paper... There is nothing written on it.
This door is locked. I wonder if I can open it somehow.
Looks like the key is inserted from the other side. If I could just get it somehow.
